s tiny walnut box with shellac and wax. #handtools #woodworking #handtoolwoodworking", "taken_at": "2016-03-27T02:03:20", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201603/82678f0bad7347caccca5f1b6825549c.jpg"}, {"caption": "Yeah! @mortise_and_tenon_mag No. 1 arrived today... great start for a weekend. @classic_hand_tools is shipping to Europe, in case you wonder where to order... #handtoolwoodworking #handtools #woodworking #mortiseandtenonmag", "taken_at": "2016-03-12T02:27:23", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201603/04c8da980ef8f218b7a90a764b7192a3.jpg"}, {"caption": "I just don't feel like working on my clamp rack... cutting ears for my wife's easter bunny decoration instead üê∞", "taken_at": "2016-03-05T08:21:51", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201603/ddb100b1c41277440cef4455197d8469.jpg"}, {"caption": "boring... #woodworking #handtools #handtoolwoodworking", "taken_at": "2016-03-05T03:42:59", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201603/bc301723329c4b967d50b69af74ecf9d.jpg"}, {"caption": "yesterday @derrhys visited my workshop and we had a nice chat about tools, workshop and upcoming projects üòÅüçª #handtools #workshop #woodworking", "taken_at": "2016-02-22T00:43:58", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201602/759212fb943fbaa704e4963a504945d7.jpg"}, {"caption": "the #spokeshave is a great tool for little woodworkers! Not easy to keep the sole flat to the wood if you're under 4 years old... but look at her sleeve, we made nice curly shavings üòä #woodworking #workshop #handtoolwoodworking #handtools", "taken_at": "2016-02-20T03:14:17", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201602/94b745b4a57fdb13d2f2b3ae7cbc56c2.jpg"}, {"caption": "Left: my old 1000/600 combination stone, right: new DMT DiaSharp diamond plate. The water stone came with a kitchen knife, never really liked it compared to other water stones. Can't wait to try the DiaSharp when I'm back from work. #handtoolwoodworking #handtools #workshop #handtoolthursday", "taken_at": "2016-02-18T00:22:59", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201602/4b8187b531410da5bcc1405bd3dcf991.jpg"}, {"caption": "I reinforced this hanger for a shelf with a dowel, as suggested by @hearth_and_homestead.brad and to my surprise some glue went through the pores of the oak üòÆ #handtoolwoodworking #handtools #woodworking #oak", "taken_at": "2016-01-31T11:58:44", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201601/1d56377f277fc4e6323019a99351ce22.jpg"}, {"caption": "Bench light in action, while I'm cutting lot's of dados for a clam rack üí°üëç #lighting #holzwerken #woodworking #workshop #handtools #handtoolwoodworking", "taken_at": "2016-01-31T09:03:12", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201601/e15538cb959dc5a2732076014f273bc6.jpg"}, {"caption": "Made a little base that fits into the dog holes for my old Ikea Lamp. üí°üëç Way better to work with proper lighting! #workshop #woodworking #holzwerken #lighting", "taken_at": "2016-01-31T08:59:26", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201601/487aaf8f5030adf439ef124d518e7599.jpg"}, {"caption": "oh wow! what a great giveaway from @vespertools. Too good not to try :) #vesper10kgiveaway", "taken_at": "2016-01-25T13:11:45", "path": "photos/201601/4a6a97db1c585a676856c36e7543d6ba.jpg"}, {"caption": "Ulmia 352 Miter Box. Most miter boxes I know are basically guided back saws, but Ulmia's is based on a frame saw... I replaced the saw guides and the blade and now it's cutting fine again. The blade is a japanese style replacement blade, looks a bit awkward to have the saw facing in the 'wrong' direction. What I really like is the fence, very accurate and sturdy. #workshop #woodworking #handtoolwoodworking #miterbox #holzwerken #Holzwerkstatt", "taken_at": "2016-01-19T00:55:43", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201601/f5cdfbeb88bcd55d8e14ce798b87eaaa.jpg"}, {"caption": "Cruising to town üòÑ The handcart makeover was a project from before IG. Ply, track saw, router, 4 coats of boat paint ... no hand tools involved. #woodworking #plywood #powertools", "taken_at": "2015-12-30T05:13:28", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201512/09b43eed7c91c433afdd43a5859490b9.jpg"}, {"caption": "This is how the hangers and the shelf go together: the slim legs get glued into dados and hopefully the rest of the hanger is thick enough not to split. (20mm / ~3/4''). #woodworking #handtoolwoodworking #handtools", "taken_at": "2015-12-28T15:21:41", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201512/9318b6aa8e043510b37d42eca5233e62.jpg"}, {"caption": "Oh noooo! I'm working on wooden clamps to attach a tray to our baby's changing table... and I managed to drop and break one after fitting the corresponding groove... stupid me! #handtools #woodworking #handtoolwoodworking #fail #stupid #oops", "taken_at": "2015-12-28T07:51:00", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201512/6fb954fd16ad29ee731c62ed5f8acfef.jpg"}, {"caption": "before glue up #woodworking #holzwerken #handtools", "taken_at": "2015-12-20T03:00:17", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201512/961271b5d258767cc6a6f761031d48f1.jpg"}, {"caption": "It‚Äôs been 5 weeks since I became father for the second time, so as a hobbyist woodworker my time in the workshop is very very limited at the moment.\nBut it always makes me happy to see all of your small and bigger projects, your tools and jigs and lots of saw dust, shavings and spirit.\nThe IG woodworking community is such a friendly, inspiring and supportive place, thank you for that! üòä\nNiels", "taken_at": "2015-12-13T15:20:54", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201512/9052ae1e68497a7ea18434104bab0ca8.jpg"}, {"caption": "Cutting grooves with a plow plane. No noise, no dust, just that satisfying *swoosh* sound üòä #holzwerken #workshop #woodworking #handtools", "taken_at": "2015-11-28T06:20:58", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201511/b33b79c94b297a1613d6562aeb4b456c.jpg"}, {"caption": "cleaning up rabbets with the router plane. It's the first time I use the spear shaped blade, works really well for me. üëç #handtools #woodworking #workshop #holzwerken", "taken_at": "2015-11-16T13:12:46", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201511/840e77cc66e79a787707ebfbf45424bc.jpg"}, {"caption": "Oh my, what a mess. I'm working on that tiny walnut box in the top left corner of the picture. #handtools #workshop #woodworking #holzwerken #handtoolthursday", "taken_at": "2015-11-05T15:03:10", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201511/5492624120714f9a8beed2687cba20c2.jpg"}, {"caption": "beautiful autumn üçÇüçÑüéÉ", "taken_at": "2015-10-31T02:07:21", "location": "Hamburg-Duvenstedt", "path": "photos/201510/727a82807785caeeecae7f40dfd9d5dd.jpg"}, {"caption": "late birthday present: my LN carcass saw now has a little sister:  the tapered dovetail saw. I really like the handles - not only the look of it, but also how it feels in my hand. I'm pretty sure I'll stick to this saw for a very long time, that's a good feeling :)", "taken_at": "2015-10-23T12:17:46", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201510/ce56d10cf018e1cccf2b40c42fa7f88b.jpg"}, {"caption": "dovetails before glue up. two turned out quite good, and two are way too loose... I still struggling with cutting the pins (tails first). After marking across the end grain, I find it hard to start the saw at the exact angle (I mean parallel and close to the line). Any suggestions? #handtools #woodworking #workshop #dovetail #holzwerken", "taken_at": "2015-10-18T09:48:55", "location": "Hamburg-Duvenstedt", "path": "photos/201510/76de57dab3a074f3dbc11845c523934e.jpg"}, {"caption": "turns out woodworking equipment is quite useful for paperworking as well :-) I'm making a little paper prototype for my day job #workshop #woodworking #handtools", "taken_at": "2015-10-16T13:11:40", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201510/115061065138c0e13c410af794357200.jpg"}, {"caption": "@overthewireless so true üòä", "taken_at": "2015-10-10T05:44:13", "location": "Hamburg-Duvenstedt", "path": "photos/201510/1c72acbd440c543f708639e5ae76e323.jpg"}, {"caption": "Soul food! Thanks for these wonderful birthday presents @linnemaman #handtools #woodworking #holzwerken #birthday #anarchisttoolchest", "taken_at": "2015-10-10T02:59:40", "location": "Hamburg-Duvenstedt", "path": "photos/201510/984da446d59ec8ef5077d044f07d9b03.jpg"}, {"caption": "Putting walnut scraps and waste to good use for the next little project: dovetail marker and saw dust for making wood filler #holzwerken #woodworking #handtools", "taken_at": "2015-10-07T13:12:51", "path": "photos/201510/d68672c5cb7a74f379eade7742a14c9b.jpg"}, {"caption": "üéâ‚ù§Ô∏è Look at that awesome birthday cake! #handtools #woodworking #holzwerken #birthday", "taken_at": "2015-10-07T09:58:47", "location": "Hamburg-Duvenstedt", "path": "photos/201510/6f5506a996d4567b4d93d07cf769855e.jpg"}, {"caption": "Any ideas what that wood is? I bought a pile of wood from a carpenter that went out of business a while ago. Some boards labeled with the woods name and some without like this one. This wood is quite easy to saw and plane. It smells like ... mhmm kind of 'old' ... could that be walnut? How to find out? #holzwerken #woodworking #handtools #wood #pleasehelp", "taken_at": "2015-10-05T12:43:08", "path": "photos/201510/a7d60242149e97c748fe2b949e53fe42.jpg"}, {"caption": "4 little blocks of pine, no big deal - but for me it's the first time that dimensioning a board by hand went so well... sawing, planing, shooting and the result is nicely true and square üòÄ So happy. Working at the new bench is such a big step forward in terms of learning.", "taken_at": "2015-10-04T08:39:38", "location": "Hamburg-Duvenstedt", "path": "photos/201510/86274ae1aafed8869daa176f0a1c1540.jpg"}, {"caption": "well ... I need a lot more practice, I guess. btw where is the wood filler filter in IG? ;) #handtools #woodworking #holzwerken", "taken_at": "2015-10-04T02:27:38", "location": "Hamburg-Duvenstedt", "path": "photos/201510/dd94e6eb504529cdca9d38bda8b1d52e.jpg"}, {"caption": "Saturday evening, why not going for some dove tail practice? #holzwerken #woodworking #handtools", "taken_at": "2015-10-03T13:39:34", "location": "Hamburg-Duvenstedt", "path": "photos/201510/dce745fec9cdab4cdad07cd9cc1f1603.jpg"}, {"caption": "I'm not the only fan of the new bench üòÉ #woodworking #workshop #holzwerken #bench #sj√∂bergs #elite1500", "taken_at": "2015-09-23T08:59:52", "location": "Hamburg, Germany", "path": "photos/201509/35243b84c6fa833aa4004c3bd28e3ab7.jpg"}, {"caption": "Tada! I've got a little bench üòÑ#sj√∂bergs #elite1500 #bench #workshop #holzwerken #woodworking", "taken_at": "2015-09-22T12:41:32", "path": "photos/201509/3d53960cb4bbbab10d748230b15a74da.jpg"}, {"caption": "my bench arrived üòÉ can't wait to assemble it üî®üîßüî© #woodworking #holzwerken #workshop #bench#sj√∂bergs #elite1500", "taken_at": "2015-09-21T11:29:29", "path": "photos/201509/c90689ff2b1ea10b16cec000dac9a733.jpg"}, {"caption": "It took quite long to decide not to build but to buy a bench, and delivery date was today. So I took a day off, but the delivery guys did not show up :( Not even a call ... and it's Friday, you know, no bench at the weekend :( #workshop #woodworking #holzwerken", "taken_at": "2015-09-18T11:30:13", "location": "Hamburg-Duvenstedt", "path": "photos/201509/9c61a0a20242745e2668791ae00d1339.jpg"}, {"caption": "unplugged lathe #woodworking", "taken_at": "2015-09-06T07:38:44", "path": "photos/201509/ccf17560a8bd244cfca42c22fbfe4d4d.jpg"}, {"caption": "thinking about buying one of these for my little workshop üòÉ#woodworking #holzwerken #workshop", "taken_at": "2015-08-08T07:26:46", "path": "photos/201508/b7cd22b80f6b8721e8c55501cd55e49e.jpg"}, {"caption": "this is the first groove I made with my plow plane ... I need much more practice to prevent tear out at the top corners. üòî Any hints? #woodworking #handtools", "taken_at": "2015-08-04T12:17:20", "path": "photos/201508/1ebf49efb85a80b6c4fea291dccbb45b.jpg"}, {"caption": "oh nice, turns out my first frame part fits into the corner üòÄ #handtools #woodworking", "taken_at": "2015-08-02T07:22:45", "path": "photos/201508/3b6369ce0b955d614caa0da8cceb576d.jpg"}, {"caption": "working on Mattea's bed ... still trying to figure out the correct angle and position for the last joint üò¨ #handtools #woodworking", "taken_at": "2015-08-02T05:33:18", "path": "photos/201508/547630ce43cdc17075e6c7a3ae2a308e.jpg"}, {"caption": "chop chop chop ... working on the frame for Mattea's bed.\nYou can do many things with #sj√∂bergs little \"smart vise\", but chopping mortises is none of them - the clamps can't stand the vibrations for long. Not the only reason to look for a proper bench and since I have so little time the next months, I think I skip building a bench and buy one. Going for smaller furniture projects instead ... on the other hand üòß ... what do you think? #workshop #woodworking #holzwerken #bench", "taken_at": "2015-07-26T12:15:15", "path": "photos/201507/bfdb32ecf7076b23e1805969637fd683.jpg"}, {"caption": "I'm building a bed for my little daughter, with lots of mortise and tenon joints. Time for a combination gauge like this one from marples, that I found on eBay... and a brand new Veritas shoulder plane, but that's another story ;-) #handtoolthursday #woodworking #holzwerken", "taken_at": "2015-07-23T10:31:15", "path": "photos/201507/fe4d103bcfca9a6cbd50c1ed14948db0.jpg"}, {"caption": "Finished this little shelf for my shop radio with milk paint and wax. I really like the result and it will make me smile every time I turn on the radio. üòÄ #woodworking #handtools #holzwerken", "taken_at": "2015-07-05T14:49:35", "path": "photos/201507/576a11e8b1907dd0ce5d6a211490707a.jpg"}, {"caption": "Little bit overcrowded that smart vise ... I definitely need a proper bench #handtools 